trans-unit.source: Specifies the type of change occurring in a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: 指定的集合中发生的更改类型<xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref>对象。

trans-unit.source: The DesignerActionListsChangedType enumeration indicates that an element has been added or removed from a managed collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objects.
trans-unit.target: DesignerActionListsChangedType 枚举指示已添加或从托管的集合中移除一个元素<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>对象。</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used in the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs> class, which is associated with the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: 此枚举用于<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs>类，该类与关联<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>事件。</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Although the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> class is a collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objects, it does not directly raise events.
trans-unit.target: 1> [!NOTE]&1;> 尽管<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>类是一套<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>对象，它不会直接引发的事件。</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>

trans-unit.source: One or more <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects have been added to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 一个或多个<xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref>对象已添加到集合。

trans-unit.source: One or more <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects have been removed from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 一个或多个<xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref>对象已从集合中移除。
